{"tid":603901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[路祭警]遭轉彎貨車夾住 女途人搶救不治","createTime":"2018-03-24T07:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T13:15:06.000Z","uid":51271,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d524d0bbbcddd3709bff682fd865a4f1dd4a3a17","tid":603901,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T07:46:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180324/57989361\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180324%2F57989361&d=ZJyhSy%2F3CVi2leHjjJ8y7QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=a3215d7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180324%2F57989361&h=77713bc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180324/57989361</a><br />\n<br />\n昨日在土瓜灣九龍城道，被貨車夾在欄杆與車身之間的姓廖女傷者(69歲)，延至昨晚11時33不治。<br />\n<br />\n昨日下午2時，一輛運載重型建築材料的貨車，司機稱改道令他行錯路進入了九龍城道，其間左轉上鄉道時太貼欄杆，將站在路邊的廖婦夾在車身與欄杆之間，68歲司機則涉嫌危險駕駛引致他人身體受嚴重傷害被捕"},{"pid":"1339e584d2c9dc5476e9e3634b9605fcda5418eb","tid":603901,"uid":70786,"like":8,"dislike":10,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"死得好<br />\n廢老亂過馬路有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af1c028cd540f4beba78bdc9c752ab4679545f2","tid":603901,"uid":125809,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"1339e584d2c9dc5476e9e3634b9605fcda5418eb","tid":603901,"uid":70786,"like":8,"dislike":10,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"死得好<br />\n廢老亂過馬路有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:18:09.000Z","msg":"個到係行人路，仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e8cb589147d54a1221206f7cc2e760ac93e58c","tid":603901,"uid":35199,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:19:00.000Z","msg":"司機好慘"},{"pid":"49cfbcc2510eeda88ba640420207f04c2594cdff","tid":603901,"uid":46332,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"3af1c028cd540f4beba78bdc9c752ab4679545f2","tid":603901,"uid":125809,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"1339e584d2c9dc5476e9e3634b9605fcda5418eb","tid":603901,"uid":70786,"like":8,"dislike":10,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"死得好<br />\n廢老亂過馬路有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:18:09.000Z","msg":"個到係行人路，仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:25:21.000Z","msg":"欄外面係應該行出去嘅咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7d0b49918fe775692de147b647fccff8ecc224","tid":603901,"uid":70063,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:26:53.000Z","msg":"路祭我是十分支持，只不過不要把你們的行動影響別人的生活與生命安全。剛剛wht app個朋友恭喜他的婆婆生日快樂，但是他給我只是一個黑暗的回覆，他說他婆婆昨天下午只有她一個人，因肚餓而落樓下用膳，但被一輛大貨車撞到重傷昏迷，然後司機說原先準備上東九龍走廊，卻遇上警察三線全封為死去同袍林海雲進行路祭，traffic jam 45分鐘後，被迫改道途經九龍城才會撞到婆婆。醫生告訴他們 你們婆婆嚴重受創，昏迷不醒，就算他日甦醒可能日後會有點問題。有點問題即係點？我只可以打一個長途電話安慰他。希望警察與其家屬們放棄你的自私，路祭你們可否不要濫用職權全封三線，？......&quot;理性啲啦！<br />\n你們雖不殺婆婆，但婆婆為你們而受傷，為左逝世既親人，而連累在生既人無辜受傷&hellip;&hellip;現在婆婆重傷昏迷，生死未卜，己所不欲勿施於人呀香港警察!!!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: large;\">司機被捕 稱不熟路</span><br />\n事發於昨下午2時許，何駕駛貨車離開啟德地盤後，駛入機場隧道準備上東九龍走廊，卻遇上當局封閉一段東九龍走廊，以便為前日車禍殉職交通警員進行路祭，車輛要改道而行。何於是駕車右轉駛出土瓜灣道後，準備出馬頭圍道繼續往東涌行程，其間疑司機不熟路而錯誤駛入了九龍城道，其間貨車左轉入下鄉道時出事。</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156225097615750&amp;set=a.10152141581235750.1073741828.687025749&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10156225097615750%26set%3Da.10152141581235750.1073741828.687025749%26type%3D3%26theater&d=ZJyhSy%2F3CVi2leHjjJ8y7QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=3112752b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156225097615750&amp;set=a.10152141581235750.1073741828.687025749&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"2da9c88325e33a21f6a3c452404cf5c68cc09f5d","tid":603901,"uid":15935,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:28:24.000Z","msg":"現代版活人陪葬"},{"pid":"a3813b010a545c53b029ef63793445ffd456b338","tid":603901,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:38:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"589e603f172f71cab3a19d4548da0d4d7bfa7764","tid":603901,"uid":55045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3813b010a545c53b029ef63793445ffd456b338","tid":603901,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"49cfbcc2510eeda88ba640420207f04c2594cdff","tid":603901,"uid":46332,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"3af1c028cd540f4beba78bdc9c752ab4679545f2","tid":603901,"uid":125809,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:18:09.000Z","msg":"個到係行人路，仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:25:21.000Z","msg":"欄外面係應該行出去嘅咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:38:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4eb65af6b7700d0bcc3d9badaa521b16482afd","tid":603901,"uid":17765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3af1c028cd540f4beba78bdc9c752ab4679545f2","tid":603901,"uid":125809,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"1339e584d2c9dc5476e9e3634b9605fcda5418eb","tid":603901,"uid":70786,"like":8,"dislike":10,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"死得好<br />\n廢老亂過馬路有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:18:09.000Z","msg":"個到係行人路，仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgm